description:
The Essential Bible Truth Treasury 3 | Jesus Christ | Episode 4 | His Names

Study 4 - His Names featuring Gottfreid Osei-Mensah.

In #3 Jesus Christ, Study 4 - His Names, the speaker is Gottfreid Osei-Mensah. Gottfreid, from Ghana, is chairman of Africa Enterprise, an itinerant speaker and former paster of a Nairobi church.

Part 3: Jesus Christ includes six programs 1. His Incarnation - Michele Guinness, 2. Main Events in the Gospels - Kully Dhadda, 3. Main Aspects of His Ministry - Michele Guinness, 4. His Names - Gottfreid Osei-Mensah, 5. His Atoning Death - Ivan Fawzi, 6. His Triumphant Resurrection - Anne Graham Lotz

"Scripture quotations taken from NIV version unless otherwise noted. Tape 3: Jesus Christ
His Incarnation - Michele Guinness
Main Events in the Gospels - Kully Dhadda
Main Aspects of His Ministry - Marion Byrne
His Names - Gottfreid Osei-Mensah
His Atoning Death - Ivan Fawzi
His Triumphant Resurrection - Anne Graham Lotz Michele Guinness is from the famous Guinness beer family.  A Jewess, converted to Christianity, she is now a well-known author and broadcaster. Kully Dhadda is an Indian journalist with the BBC. Gottfreid Osei-Mensah, from Ghana, is chairman of Africa Enterprise, an itinerant speaker and former pastor of a Nairobi church. Ivan Fawzi, formerly a communist in Iraq, was converted and now teaches theology in London. Anne Graham Lotz is the daughter of evangelist Billy Graham and a well-known writer and speaker."

Director: Crawford Telfer
Starring: Gottfreid Osei-Mensah
